  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.747599602684121        -20.3432          -469.13         -1962.82
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.238913319517069         -6.5012          -149.92          -627.27
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.028087216477431          0.7643            17.62            73.74
